item.title: About me
item.description: Hey there, im EinsKatze aka. Pascal. Currently I am doing an apprenticeship as an IT specialist for system integration. Im interested in Linux, Internet Privacy and Coding. As you may have already noticed from my other profiles such as discord or github, i really like cats. I may add a little more to this page soon™️, but as of now, i don’t now what else you would like to know about me.
